      rating: 4.5,
      numReviews: 10,
      description: 'high quality pant',

    {
      name: 'Adidas fit pant',
      slug: 'Adidas-fit-pant',
      category: 'pants',
      image: '/images/p1.jpg',
      price: 120,
      countInStock: 10,
      brand: 'Adidas',
      rating: 4.5,
      numReviews: 10,
      description: 'high quality pant',
    },
  ],
};

export default data;
